Poetic Babu Help Menu
Syntax: ~set prefix <prefixes...> Alias: ~set prefixes
Sets Poetic Babu's global prefix(es).
Warning: This is not additive. It will replace all current prefixes. See also the --mentionable flag to enable mentioning the bot as the prefix. Examples: - ~set prefix ! - ~set prefix "! " - Quotes are needed to use spaces in prefixes. - ~set prefix "@Poetic Babu " - This uses a mention as the prefix. See also the --mentionable flag. - ~set prefix ! ? . - Sets multiple prefixes. Arguments: - <prefixes...> - The prefixes the bot will respond to globally.
Type ~help <command> for more info on a command. You can also type ~help <category> for more info on a category.
